 ạlqrạr- yqwlwạ mtạʿb yqwlwạ kwạrtẖ wạnạ mṭmn wbạlrạḥh ḥạss
 lạ̉n ạ̹lhy fy qlby jạls hw ạbwyạ wbhmwmy ḥạss
